Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:06.19,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Why does the scent of the rain make me feel nostalgic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:11.84,Translation,,0,0,0,,Why does my heart clamor as summer approaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:17.50,Translation,,0,0,0,,Why do I cry when people laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:23.13,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it all right to think that even so I’ll be rewarded someday?”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:29.32,Translation,,0,0,0,,With the word “goodbye” tearing so much at my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:37.32,Translation,,0,0,0,,I was standing still for just a few moments at sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:40.37,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Teacher, I want to talk about my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.88,Translation,,0,0,0,,What should I do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:47.78,Translation,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to tell me ‘no one knows that’ or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:51.48,Translation,,0,0,0,,Look, it’s not that I want to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.51,Translation,,0,0,0,,I just want to live without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:58.05,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it selfish to just want to look at the blue sky?”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:16.79,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Why do I lie even though it makes my heart ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:22.40,Translation,,0,0,0,,Why do only bad people prosper?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:28.05,Translation,,0,0,0,,Why is it that the character for ‘happiness’ includes the ￥ sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:33.95,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it on purpose that leaving out a single stroke turns it into the character for ‘pain’?”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.65,Translation,,0,0,0,,With a price sticker saying “youth” stuck to my back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:47.85,Translation,,0,0,0,,I was hoping in some way for Hitchcock-like suspense
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.98,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Teacher, I don’t care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.46,Translation,,0,0,0,,Just going on living causes me pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:58.32,Translation,,0,0,0,,Neither Nietzche nor Freud wrote about how to fill this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:01.88,Translation,,0,0,0,,I just want to close my eyes in the scent of summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.09,Translation,,0,0,0,,And sketch out the height of the clouds with my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:08.62,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it selfish to just want to relive memories?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:24.52,Translation,,0,0,0,,“A story where people die dramatically will sell, won’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:29.88,Translation,,0,0,0,,I’ve come to hate that even the moment that a flower’s petals fall has a price on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.06,Translation,,0,0,0,,What was your dream, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.65,Translation,,0,0,0,,Did you forget it when you became an adult?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.34,Translation,,0,0,0,,“Teacher, I want to talk about my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.11,Translation,,0,0,0,,What should I do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:52.03,Translation,,0,0,0,,‘Tears make people stronger’ was nothing but sophism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:58.39,Translation,,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s not that I don’t care what happens to me, it’s just that reality is flickering,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.18,Translation,,0,0,0,,And summer is far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:04.37,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is this really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.14,Translation,,0,0,0,,Can I go on living like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:11.72,Translation,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to tell me ‘only you can answer that’ or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.69,Translation,,0,0,0,,I just want to close my eyes in the scent of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.48,Translation,,0,0,0,,I want to feel the wind always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:22.41,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it selfish to just want to look at the blue sky?”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.69,Translation,,0,0,0,,Is it selfish if I just want to know you?
